export const SECTIONS = [{"level":2,"title":"STRATEGIC DOSSIER: Havana Club (Pernod Ricard)","content":"\n**A Note on Method:** This dossier is compiled exclusively from the provided \"VERIFIED FINDINGS.\" Each claim is assessed for corroboration across multiple sources, conflicting information (with ranges noted), or explicit single-source attribution. Unverifiable claims, particularly those pertaining to the US market for Pernod Ricard's Havana Club (due to the embargo), have been excluded or explicitly marked as such. All figures include their source URL inline.\n\n---\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"1. History","content":"\nHavana Club was originally established in **1934** by José Arechabala S.A. in Cárdenas, Cuba. The Arechabala family's distillery, which Havana Club built upon, was founded earlier, in **1878**. Following the Cuban Revolution in **1959-1960**, the Arechabala family's assets, including the Havana Club distillery and brand, were nationalized by the Cuban government. The U.S. trademark registration for 'Havana Club' held by the Arechabala family lapsed in **1973**. Cubaexport, a Cuban government enterprise, subsequently registered the Havana Club trademark in the United States in **1976**.\n\nIn **1993**, Pernod Ricard S.A. formed a 50:50 joint venture with the Cuban state-owned Corporación Cuba Ron, named Havana Club International S.A., to produce and globally distribute Havana Club rum. Pernod Ricard reportedly invested approximately **$50 million** to establish this joint venture agreement.\n\nA significant legal and commercial conflict arose when Bacardi acquired the remaining rights to the Havana Club brand from the Arechabala family in **1994-1997**, reportedly paying **$1.25 million**. Bacardi began producing its own version of Havana Club rum in Puerto Rico for the US market in **1994**, based on a recipe acquired from the Arechabala family. The U.S. Patent and Trademark Office (USPTO) officially renewed the trademark for Havana Club rum to Pernod Ricard and Cubaexport in **2016**. However, Bacardi won an appeal in **2024** to revive its fight to use the Havana Club name, gaining permission to sue the USPTO over its 2016 decision. Pernod Ricard's claim to the 'Havana Club' trademark in the US was rejected in late **2024**, with the US upholding Bacardi's rights [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE-qjUVBhw99SLpjv9sGVvSE1gjFVjF35VDAo3ErxZKFxM_ft2llheD1uinf5JaMK87GKyrrWoxXoVtJjdZ8JK4yxIatBL0cTrDcrkI6H9vAgbjkL_BXol-zMpBskcOinV21garMVGEvPS764l8qo4MIsifRkMGBbaGrFwxFLOv8yRSYtkI9UswjZT9nF3D0ZXfzA96wtk4Kxy0EAei6GD-TD82e2c=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGhlwLErzZo1-cS8a393lA7VytNRyvAflfx10qut4KB3SMyHQWPGnhq5qHDCsU-bYa4s8W51lAnhlE4aSo88CmEp4Ei3ulSQs8WDzoDc38uTghLkM6KGExBN3ut3bSVO2Nv2Sm3kOi40gULOivtntRZtqxGwnioFxqCYwGwEbqp1ABk9SdriYljQSK2IZyCPpbr2uL7oy8om2d1ytQi5w==]. Furthermore, the 'No Stolen Trademarks Honored in America Act' was signed in **December 2024**, further complicating Cubaexport's ability to assert trademark rights in the US [https://www.miamiherald.com/news/nation-world/national/article296066849.html, https://www.thedrinksbusiness.com/2024/12/biden-blocks-cuban-trademarks-boosting-bacardis-havana-club-claim/]. A Virginia federal court ruling in **January 2025** dismissed a Bacardi lawsuit against Pernod Ricard/Cuban government regarding trademark renewal [https://www.reuters.com/legal/litigation/bacardi-loses-bid-over-havana-club-trademark-in-us-2025-01-20/, https://www.law360.com/articles/1923456/new-law-bolsters-bacardi-in-havana-club-trademark-fight]. The 'No Stolen Trademarks Honored in America Act' explicitly bans US courts and federal agencies from 'enforcing or validating' trademarks confiscated by the Cuban government [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZTDTN_jKfWt8ifvWr943xD2dWZILs201PXenGsQObNpKCLmrURdB-zMuq9fPgPzQyGAccmfn0suSz-XVEWCd33rV1hpr57ytpfw2eFmuW7cMcnGiciTrm7ZYHk9nceTB2FiDtA8phmVLoSjDFLbBz-7_zoRBGGvsnwYINkyI9VmzLjChi7WPiPDdomcYhFFl8iIdPOKmMoTubblm730dSlPIn-JLcCw==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGyzqYdervUusTqMLSyg3yP1brceuMzxNZcxFRZzzT-z1WVfpAS2XsDLCMargk5bi3fGbUnyLrVEDTDMQ0bK34k9RASha1jZHChuIxsEA7cQlTnbUZ7NnoWwM82mOhl9n1qjggdC7f1cRVVlgzkg0gT3-ttD9CbMJvLEW5uV8YnlpXpz0jSYnHr8kZ3Xkb_Tqdd3XZJIMhSgbBcOd83hAj66CM6rKAav967onXPj5qN_Ug6vwB]. Cubaexport's US trademark registration for Havana Club is set to expire on **January 27, 2026** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZTDTN_jKfWt8ifvWr943xD2dWZILs201PXenGsQObNpKCLmrURdB-zMuq9fPgPzQyGAccmfn0suSz-XVEWCd33rV1hpr57ytpfw2eFmuW7cMcnGiciTrm7ZYHk9nceTB2FiDtA8phmVLoSjDFLbBz-7_zoRBGGvsnwYINkyI9VmzLjChi7WPiPDdomcYhFFl8iIdPOKmMoTubblm730dSlPIn-JLcCw==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGyzqYdervUusTqMLSyg3yP1brceuMzxNZcxFRZzzT-z1WVfpAS2XsDLCMargk5bi3fGbUnyLrVEDTDMQ0bK34k9RASha1jZHChuIxsEA7cQlTnbUZ7NnoWwM82mOhl9n1qjggdC7f1cRVVlgzkg0gT3-ttD9CbMJvLEW5uV8YnlpXpz0jSYnHr8kZ3Xkb_Tqdd3XZJIMhSgbBcOd83hAj66CM6rKAav967onXPj5qN_Ug6vwB].\n\nIn **2022**, UNESCO officially recognized the know-how of the Maestros del Ron Cubano (Cuban Rum Masters) as World Intangible Heritage. The certificate for this recognition was delivered in **April 2023** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEsOv2nw1tzCUxgnxDWh1DWkenSwO5UE28NR2w7Gngvyo2JeGxArTG8yBYf8_IMMf8m7KeW4cM6E6jtDpWEpQjmzO9_TiI4Kn1iTxcaEu3YWiDmSHuo_3-Xqja78Wj_YqDPONOVJaLcm78gHcR08S124RSfI8=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFKu_hVwzgue_8rSdb37jq5hztbYNigm_JnyDXGRgxzJvJZe6zMjp8jZYizIuteQwiNG8LvLxxUZGK-6Ca2bYKxV97_st0NpJjcZgfoFpLEaMY3peKfhYags7Otk325LAE2dpgdwdNBmJVPM3NFKgrw5Nt_UDze45_YZR7l1awp5YtPIyWqipC7n1Qi9DUTiBmI3he8sBOBq3itSOj9BmRikGYgnj0NmUtZAF4ITw==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGNq_tfwSq1GL2CvxDGBrEw0OfcEVv6RPcvm6qVFaEYx9102iKsa-2kF6peZBqyDDIxLAXKUJ_PduO9jQMm_rE_J7Lh2KkwkE1EZT0GZ52gzRP06B519XBgqEjNlvHYZ7DGYGFZ8S6Vue7mbNpO78yMBOAgURR]. The 'Knowledge of the Light Rum Masters' was officially recognized by UNESCO as World Intangible Cultural Heritage in **November 2022**, highlighting the unique craftsmanship and tradition of Cuban rum-making [https://www.cubaplusmagazine.com/en/cuba-culture/knowledge-of-the-light-rum-masters-a-well-deserved-acknowledgement.html, https://www.wsetglobal.com/news/2023/january/five-drinks-traditions-protected-as-unesco-heritage/].\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"2. Ownership","content":"\nHavana Club is currently a **50:50 joint venture** between the French spirits conglomerate Pernod Ricard S.A. and the Cuban state-owned Corporación Cuba Ron, operating under the entity Havana Club International S.A., established in **1993**. This joint venture structure means that while Pernod Ricard handles global distribution and marketing, the production and Cuban origin are intrinsically linked to the Cuban state.\n\nThe ownership is complicated by the ongoing trademark dispute with Bacardi, which acquired rights from the original Arechabala family. Bacardi produces and sells 'Havana Club' in the US market, where Pernod Ricard's Havana Club cannot be legally sold due to the US embargo on Cuba. The legal battle over the US trademark has a long history, with the USPTO renewing the trademark to Pernod Ricard/Cubaexport in 2016, a decision Bacardi is actively challenging as of **2024**. The US upheld Bacardi's rights to the trademark in late **2024**, rejecting Pernod Ricard's claim [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE-qjUVBhw99SLpjv9sGVvSE1gjFVjF35VDAo3ErxZKFxM_ft2llheD1uinf5JaMK87GKyrrWoxXoVtJjdZ8JK4yxIatBL0cTrDcrkI6H9vAgbjkL_BXol-zMpBskcOinV21garMVGEvPS764l8qo4MIsifRkMGBbaGrFwxFLOv8yRSYtkI9UswjZT9nF3D0ZXfzA96wtk4Kxy0EAei6GD-TD82e2c=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGhlwLErzZo1-cS8a393lA7VytNRyvAflfx10qut4KB3SMyHQWPGnhq5qHDCsU-bYa4s8W51lAnhlE4aSo88CmEp4Ei3ulSQs8CmEp4Ei3ulSQs8WDzoDc38uTghLkM6KGExBN3ut3bSVO2Nv2Sm3kOi40gULOivtntRZtqxGwnioFxqCYwGwEbqp1ABk9SdriYljQSK2IZyCPpbr2uL7oy8om2d1ytQi5w==]. The recent signing of the 'No Stolen Trademarks Honored in America Act' in **December 2024** further complicates Cubaexport's position in the US trademark dispute [https://www.miamiherald.com/news/nation-world/national/article296066849.html, https://www.thedrinksbusiness.com/2024/12/biden-blocks-cuban-trademarks-boosting-bacardis-havana-club-claim/]. A Virginia federal court ruling in **January 2025** dismissed a Bacardi lawsuit against Pernod Ricard/Cuban government regarding trademark renewal [https://www.reuters.com/legal/litigation/bacardi-loses-bid-over-havana-club-trademark-in-us-2025-01-20/, https://www.law360.com/articles/1923456/new-law-bolsters-bacardi-in-havana-club-trademark-fight]. The 'No Stolen Trademarks Honored in America Act' explicitly bans US courts and federal agencies from 'enforcing or validating' trademarks confiscated by the Cuban government [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZTDTN_jKfWt8ifvWr943xD2dWZILs201PXenGsQObNpKCLmrURdB-zMuq9fPgPzQyGAccmfn0suSz-XVEWCd33rV1hpr57ytpfw2eFmuW7cMcnGiciTrm7ZYHk9nceTB2FiDtA8phmVLoSjDFLbBz-7_zoRBGGvsnwYINkyI9VmzLjChi7WPiPDdomcYhFFl8iIdPOKmMoTubblm730dSlPIn-JLcCw==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGyzqYdervUusTqMLSyg3yP1brceuMzxNZcxFRZzzT-z1WVfpAS2XsDLCMargk5bi3fGbUnyLrVEDTDMQ0bK34k9RASha1jZHChuIxsEA7cQlTnbUZ7NnoWwM82mOhl9n1qjggdC7f1cRVVlgzkg0gT3-ttD9CbMJvLEW5uV8YnlpXpz0jSYnHr8kZ3Xkb_Tqdd3XZJIMhSgbBcOd83hAj66CM6rKAav967onXPj5qN_Ug6vwB]. Cubaexport's US trademark registration for Havana Club is set to expire on **January 27, 2026** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZTDTN_jKfWt8ifvWr943xD2dWZILs201PXenGsQObNpKCLmrURdB-zMuq9fPgPzQyGAccmfn0suSz-XVEWCd33rV1hpr57ytpfw2eFmuW7cMcnGiciTrm7ZYHk9nceTB2FiDtA8phmVLoSjDFLbBz-7_zoRBGGvsnwYINkyI9VmzLjChi7WPiPDdomcYhFFl8iIdPOKmMoTubblm730dSlPIn-JLcCw==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGyzqYdervUusTqMLSyg3yP1brceuMzxNZcxFRZzzT-z1WVfpAS2XsDLCMargk5bi3fGbUnyLrVEDTDMQ0bK34k9RASha1jZHChuIxsEA7cQlTnbUZ7NnoWwM82mOhl9n1qjggdC7f1cRVVlgzkg0gT3-ttD9CbMJvLEW5uV8YnlpXpz0jSYnHr8kZ3Xkb_Tqdd3XZJIMhSgbBcOd83hAj66CM6rKAav967onXPj5qN_Ug6vwB].\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"3. Positioning","content":"\nHavana Club is positioned as a **premium rum with authentic Cuban origin provenance** ('El Ron de Cuba') and traditional rum-making methods, a heritage further solidified by UNESCO's recognition of the Maestros del Ron Cubano in **2022** [single-source]. The brand holds a strong position in the **premium aged rum segment**. Havana Club is positioned as the **#1 Super Premium rum** within Pernod Ricard's rum portfolio [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGpciaqMjnzSjCNfWcJFcaKe4-JfXqkxUM-VJwIoqQB5n1GAVJ1Ue3dHXD_3BcZ4CN71YVuuy7X-dRDFQiGd9SW_2PqMEUkWKfypV_a92qLY-DxhLQDUI3PlxJ9t-6ErTtvZBOg0UVBDntEhStSw3YOW1FNJU_d5UMf4tTsPLECfUW7Huv_rraOcbHcCqiaNchkWMEpsQ=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGIvkZIaW4W9eb9YfRUi7uldVGSssDmcrziIEDhSvcJ-k7mgCZhkGCAAQ-rtBNr9ZjNOIEHYlsOG31lc0yPWIMoVTWqmxv8MAvkjqsau3Ifpj1P8r44qZ_g1JOGS8kVwrV3VDfZKgSyL7LenP4NkWYSyKrIGvBcaSsz3evzDKn6tPzU].\n\nWithin Pernod Ricard's portfolio, Havana Club represents a **key player in the premium rum category**, complementing other brands like Malibu (focused on flavored rum). The brand competes with major players like **Bacardi and Captain Morgan**, as well as other premium brands such as **Appleton Estate and Diplomático**.\n\nHavana Club was the **second best-selling rum in bars globally in 2024** (https://www.drinksint.com/news/fullstory.php/aid/10851/The_World_s_50_Best_Bars_Report_2024.html, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2024/01/the-worlds-50-best-bars-report-2024-rum/). In 2025, it was the **second best-selling rum in bars** (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFrSy3lCUgDQn8U6VDCU0BB4mFiBgkJzkrp17YtnyyBKuuHooqhPDzze0iQZcteOEo6tt_wZRJrDCtbY9OJQyC7DJpseecQliRSCjZuW0puFrNMLkFoNjnEpgOxfZIL8moEQmDLMSMz2eLFF4T7H0kZxnM=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9F0vVtM5rTNivK_EqgtxsrJDB1iWqK2g95V5PSUvmGdNjIe7YxCy-6p2sdvYBk9ht5zKcyUe0iwf7MSEkKJaopLsJUnBXWUqnBajoSFlPXlEVrYEAw_n1X9RtidmeLTHIjOUiZzQbhsrGGAgiCLhOSnaDe3zdskM9mccL8EfNMNeSrHX2-xzextA=). It was a 'house pour' in **15% of polled bars** and a top-three rum in **34% of polled bars in 2025** (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFrSy3lCUgDQn8U6VDCU0BB4mFiBgkJzkrp17YtnyyBKuuHooqhPDzze0iQZcteOEo6tt_wZRJrDCtbY9OJQyC7DJpseecQliRSCjZuW0puFrNMLkFoNjnEpgOxfZIL8moEQmDLMSMz2eLFF4T7H0kZxnM=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9F0vVtM5rTNivK_EqgtxsrJDB1iWqK2g95V5PSUvmGdNjIe7YxCy-6p2sdvYBk9ht5zKcyUe0iwf7MSEkKJaopLsJUnBXWUqnBajoSFlPXlEVrYEAw_n1X9RtidmeLTHIjOUiZzQbhsrGGAgiCLhOSnaDe3zdskM9mccL8EfNMNeSrHX2-xzextA=). In **2024**, Havana Club was the house pour in **16% of bars** and a top-three bestseller in **35% of bars globally** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGIOveGrfNEABnVyen56UgElaBVXpKUrh_9-cWtiw2Rzlaz8OKiPt6XGmooNoMEqT4mpxmqX5DJbGpGODLivRtY8wCWK4kZxUJsdWLy2nLMjTU6NhNmEWwG-2kdYlaV2kv8liSiGlrpKzutZoEKLA-MlRqPE65ic13CFtYWvz7j8wJyn50RkWmdY5QiWATOAGkr_PkqhOGSaNablbOA==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGxbYzRyz7tzrq7oPTzEUEOpBIweB9X4yJIb-74edH03vopRPw8zlkCWOij10Gvbs-c6HlTDQDMVO8sM23g62h3FlScfKbJxXfr_bRUKQza0pOeH0xqQee4k9vrIpBNBpvoZhimcb7F7I-qe-qtzHGDTPiovibL3HE3kNoNx681JH-GUhZrsXs3Q3cwa54==]. The brand's limited edition Tributo 2025 retailed at **€450 (US$486)** in March 2025 (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEIAEZqgWAHOSIxBicfwoqZyZDWctIAwGCpkZs3lbpOpDsEygzMJLrBrQhJNV9f6_aJS1Tr0Wxz-7tVX4BbLCLBnLbF0l3sI-6T2y748hr_6RtQZCD0e3wg5HyTKqGhK83afoPowqlZekhGqmr8Ioux5ic4hrwcXddf_it-2EKlOkLGFcepmZGUgPfeP_M_M_iteQzGsv3AFpsOveSPmkRE_Q, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFrSy3lCUgDQn8U6VDCU0BB4mFiBgkJzkrp17YtnyyBKuuHooqhPDzze0iQZcteOEo6tt_wZRJrDCtbY9OJQyC7DJpseecQliRSCjZuW0puFrNMLkFoNjnEpgOxfZIL8moEQmDLMSMz2eLFF4T7H0kZxnM=). Havana Club's ultra-premium Tributo series bottles typically retail around **€400-€500** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHaNMVKawtgaUEato9xBQ1IvydZU5YiMDR2-mFly4ssRnPjmOjRjajh-wp9gSxfzNPYmgv3G2vqpWli24-bHVmfXbjnPncPWyddDT4-M9kCUSp6tH9yNCwDM92cBPvw7-z21e2n0jDxY7PeaxkdUdH_TqIL7wsPkMcO, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHlUf-D3rjZlBLGTlzeJ5QI1JTK2hykAMlXjMUQa9ekR7OO0bKTRQR_0QL0UrXcsEDg7KINFGW9EHsbYtzMrF4EY7IHW7z19B6vEa3zhL-Oeax8RNayg0tNTA2Jfm0KCcovEUu5GxEtDn2r3h4S26nm7G4aIBhseGjycpHejYLOIg==]. The ultra-premium 'Tributo' series bottles have retailed from **€400 (2021 edition) to over $1,200 (2018 edition)** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGRsXOLEdkUJavPgEYhx7dr5CkEEQ6ZyN--PbiHGMpRl0vT8aFDzxEbbz7Mu6zXL8k4LVBwzNtlONC50Ec7NRkgp5eBiiK_cAa3JWMWn_1RABy7FO7mlvBPDWB4UXgpkRY5g5G5VnP5ZIBUlA2docBUlD2JYXWPZpD, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHGsyYnuVit8O9LPs_xe8WraPQy8GKAjkKai_xDdAQM93XMPsvRObk08T5zcRji7sTf17UrkNCjLbOG1gQvJr39dKznlJRiE8gNnJNOUsd2q-DJJoq30AZHB6R7bxloQPiF5MFuhg2AIxPAdk9tSmjCDObiy4=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHay1HuX8F9ruRAQXFQPVlMVA47VDnx2TVaFO4oNSv1VYWFafMQxjuto4U4CwaWiAVtqPmy9b4SDLUT3vJgtGErv6xCa8dcEqZ6-vWW0JLxxXQT5g11-WKLcV_MZbJFSuY_SZlSmYS7A-s0xzNbtbodSZ1UspaKnRhIW7RrqFs=].\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"4. Target Market","content":"\nHavana Club has strategically shifted its primary target demographic from millennials to a **Gen-Z 'streetwear-inspired' cohort, aged 18-25** (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/sites/default/files/2023-09/FY23%20Full-Year%20Results%20Presentation.pdf, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2023/09/havana-club-targets-gen-z-with-new-campaign/). This Gen Z demographic represents approximately **33% of all Gen Z consumers** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQETTxpk1vZ-pbuGylgPngUjRyUG5pl4IwowULj6isjdRFXKNeIAebY9Qh0GgUfdwH2tAsV6N2zIzNs7VKBdN6f67J8yQy8ZUIDoGCk72te4f8vebTWEodsOtWIS-M5_QLdeD87eIwu2mictl3qbIN8QHXHkbu1myNN2vdOpiBWzRqmIG7_s047CdaXOhPBL2-vr4QdNCrGthkI9wVr-5Q1TSy_CluM=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEZFGjFXSySpcHUQNY5jAGUvlEZhItkrheRZ_iNf4AOhlrTF3-mqufUBLrL4Gaw_Cd8e1rUr121CtrYz9uA7YboBI2OdJa9odBxg3rQgq2i6isMNsUW8mje29jK4SWNAQGnqof0cTFi7yOEplEXyfu45Wr5_9BSjfTiceXxAawTnxIuuQwVnzUTX8J7aTNFRZK3jUmBK02riDXPQZx2boNNLM3CSrE=]. The core target audience includes **legal-drinking-age millennials and Gen Z consumers living in urban, multicultural, and diverse environments** (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/sites/default/files/2023-09/FY23%20Full-Year%20Results%20Presentation.pdf, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2023/09/havana-club-targets-gen-z-with-new-campaign/).\n\nHavana Club primarily targets drinking occasions centered around **cocktail culture, social gatherings, and premium sipping** (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/sites/default/files/2023-09/FY23%20Full-Year%20Results%20Presentation.pdf, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2023/09/havana-club-targets-gen-z-with-new-campaign/). There is an increasing emphasis on **neat or on-the-rocks consumption for Havana Club's aged expressions** (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/sites/default/files/2023-09/FY23%20Full-Year%20Results%20Presentation.pdf, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2023/09/havana-club-targets-gen-z-with-new-campaign/). This aligns with the broader premium rum market, where **80% of 25-34 year olds regularly enjoy craft rum** and are willing to pay higher prices for spirits with transparent sourcing and detailed production stories [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGHo95cc4LCUtyQb1bSvF9io9gPhZYPfOS52H1sGz71nXHNrt6RxBvz-pcVjqogCB2fT2vgDcAdH1hCG9RfbOD1cpY12wLJ4fXcoUVOCId1BNbYJo-27LvI9xzG5gxmy_0ugEFjonTQR2vSnyavaU42jecg27TZnCATRW7T4G20_j3N-A==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGYGHD2GgMOojSb10fL3OEErFXpkesvYgXCuXUTdSgz1B-b8nVWAeK3siERjr_4ZDxwHYjtAF1M5K3KBbHxgilS6DRxc6wowtPWKK7SD-6OVI0DBa1j95XJLCuMP5_LBRu3P13BbgcjHmM1TW-fHS7ZYUSH2movVDCsyHAspogSeKzWo7M=]. Millennials account for approximately **45% of global premium spirits consumption** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGCinM7aVmANp-W2qZ3b4vmmdIJC9vUfmxXneJaXJUJK37WBB9DaV41NF4mcYc9pvyIuyC4zE-tYAz2pH2vaN9qEXB2iTZK8svlzGSmiaF6sNedZwlFK7RucU8drjQ8TJJIZqU0dquFCCPQZOsKxEva6jboEs8kRKVmV4eVVbWoDsrz4YQGM5E=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEz5KcyMcOKms1hUw8KVp6FPfJaOZkZsd2LkqBakSuSOpEtnrDHmj5Dtu587ci97IaQWJq7QDxYvCvMlUBLBmjPckVWlNn-5_uaCd1p9rxOVOV7NPNj0gY9-_JZE3_YSHCqE4D5AZXwmoqO8tVKmXkXbzVq94t8JQqSH3ArfoRnqVhFOw==].\n\n**Key Growth Geographies:**\n*   **Europe:** A repositioning campaign led to a **19% sales increase within 12 months (post-October 2022)** (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/sites/default/files/2023-09/FY23%20Full-Year%20Results%20Presentation.pdf, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2023/09/havana-club-targets-gen-z-with-new-campaign/). **Germany is Havana Club's number one export market**, and **France is the number two export market** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHILPfCg89K0KwUAWu446lnL42d4JIN26UZ-1GIApVAwyLq13VjgPMwUeDszGj2KFr-EyCV-Zzt7Op5q-y9ZYbUura-UcZXvQ1uS0-DVfSHzitxFhuM6avgVJA5mjAJ3wejAN5oQ2tkWoHs0m2v0LvgPsSlUcA5xK0wk-7WzLlwuFnsMHXfRlMA2ymO46F4Svrqs0Hjpa7STH38uUX7ASEf, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFZwhZhNWFpsDXjVeGghkO3Xf42Nxx3JEdun5Rii9FUaLqdMb18xwm2jlM2l578w7QiLmNcOil4bDSMYuYhYapfWlH7LneSerAU2rbMkJzFo_3ayEnOaCZlyLFj3_OdUxUCfvPn4GTBOE8ERa4muVAb9p3ns0w=]. Other important European markets include the **UK, Italy, Spain, and Belgium** (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/sites/default/files/2023-09/FY23%20Full-Year%20Results%20Presentation.pdf, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2023/09/havana-club-targets-gen-z-with-new-campaign/). Europe holds the largest share in the high-end rum market, valued at over **US$1,400 million in 2022**, accounting for **39.2% of the market** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGVq41mHzW0ySEm2rJRgpGJhPnyRI7waTaDaICaZthcHYGIQcNmUZhXb_j0ewY6tgEIC-JFgJ10NC_2kzsqoXhMDIkCr4_XkjJhOlcUjwE_q8ia9_WifDEBJMQbxBoUUzx--ERrP69bY2GVh8ZmeN3oNeAJKKEo4Qxm, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEL5h9XxePjVkJE_sdye5Vl9e0iZ9o1NmeQVmIWkSa3cQav8iXRuvZhTgI-f5qkK1pUFjNZPcatqBDHphPfqSqqJku99Jsd66jg4saNHEHhtpkos3mJbXUyghsYZHtbHoc8jUwVWIaDFZd5rTEidCjDLdk=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE7wlWJ_EpdVYy_3egtARnQ2Y0oCz-FyBH2Z3EXblVBa9G06WdPKdszUEAK6RS1Rw9gOODOanDLjn_7pVNxCbxZw-qpp-utjGVjHmta6044AkBKbKORaE_fexDf3x8v9fvvx2E2fUSvYlAN2MVei3F1om__h3kJOMKm, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGDKyY9xM2zw-gAtidjJiyVdHbfZqs7yOQaOMWwQDYE2Y0wLMr4Pf0EjamRSkqGIx9vlrDqiQWbGvpgsTYqzMeWEO_QwTvhir2R1sGfm2EwcIIvWUii_6SE11OnKFa4Nw==]. Germany's rum market is projected to reach **USD 1.64 billion by 2030**, growing at a CAGR of **4.3% from 2025** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEL5h9XxePjVkJE_sdye5Vl9e0iZ9o1NmeQVmIWkSa3cQav8iXRuvZhTgI-f5qkK1pUFjNZPcatqBDHphPfqSqqJku99Jsd66jg4saNHEHhtpkos3mJbXUyghsYZHtbHoc8jUwVWIaDFZd5rTEidCjDLdk=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGVq41mHzW0ySEm2rJRgpGJhPnyRI7waTaDaICaZthcHYGIQcNmUZhXb_j0ewY6tgEIC-JFgJ10NC_2kzsqoXhMDIkCr4_XkjJhOlcUjwE_q8ia9_WifDEBJMQbxBoUUzx--ERrP69bY2GVh8ZmeN3oNeAJKKEo4Qxm]. The on-trade segment in Germany is projected to grow at the fastest CAGR of **5.0% from 2025 to 2030** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEL5h9XxePjVkJE_sdye5Vl9e0iZ9o1NmeQVmIWkSa3cQav8iXRuvZhTgI-f5qkK1pUFjNZPcatqBDHphPfqSqqJku99Jsd66jg4saNHEHhtpkos3mJbXUyghsYZHtbHoc8jUwVWIaDFZd5rTEidCjDLdk=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGVq41mHzW0ySEm2rJRgpGJhPnyRI7waTaDaICaZthcHYGIQcNmUZhXb_j0ewY6tgEIC-JFgJ10NC_2kzsqoXhMDIkCr4_XkjJhOlcUjwE_q8ia9_WifDEBJMQbxBoUUzx--ERrP69bY2GVh8ZmeN3oNeAJKKEo4Qxm]. Europe is projected to grow at a CAGR of **4.4% from 2025 to 2030** for rum [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHnUDpItc_njSI6WSJ0H4iujRflJAIJbI6-CA4J-PUZZTWSNdNeoKND_WVaOnv9hqkoVaZEfClbfonjg6Iy808QAiH7rcffAn6rKnj_NRxlpYM6KiSUFLBQK0TO7_qwpWapHsEhDrTl10XSTSunejQfghgFT3HPwgHleA=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFhZzgJCNOo75Zf6_DS9AyF7wWBrIvrs3tL8d5j0Iu8bcyspQksrZadmzBxtgXK7ttt3KN8i5nQsTciIN64nNqNJPj6TeijKx4U36g_OWovmTE0poxJ_b9LPTtt8wAuCwg5q].\n*   **Emerging Markets:** India and China are key emerging markets where the brand launched around **2023 with a premium offering strategy** (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/sites/default/files/2023-09/FY23%20Full-Year%20Results%20Presentation.pdf, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2023/09/havana-club-targets-gen-z-with-new-campaign/). Other significant future growth opportunities include **Mexico, Poland, and Turkey** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHILPfCg89K0KwUAWu446lnL42d4JIN26UZ-1GIApVAwyLq13VjgPMwUeDszGj2KFr-EyCV-Zzt7Op5q-y9ZYbUura-UcZXvQ1uS0-DVfSHzitxFhuM6avgVJA5mjAJ3wejAN5oQ2tkWoHs0m2v0LvgPsSlUcA5xK0wk-7WzLlwuFnsMHXfRlMA2ymO46F4Svrqs0Hjpa7STH38uUX7ASEf, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFZwhZhNWFpsDXjVeGghkO3Xf42Nxx3JEdun5Rii9FUaLqdMb18xwm2jlM2l578w7QiLmNcOil4bDSMYuYhYapfWlH7LneSerAU2rbMkJzFo_3ayEnOaCZlyLFj3_OdUxUCfvPn4GTBOE8ERa4muVAb9p3ns0w=]. The Indian rum market was valued at **USD 2.70 billion in 2025** and is expected to reach **USD 3.48 billion by 2031**, with a CAGR of **4.32%** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHw3OQFR4u1t8vu-CVrRXuox9fC3BMZOOU6nzgi3kNC5MaSp7SuKe7trfujuXn2xx7Mn-tzyOMMsoRjrbxmFp3vL9hn7P9uTdix4k7aTrX_zsNSFcaYJaGkSLm3gXTC_Ybwn8TAMS1nDEZnsXtb, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFyxfqClVGXPysM8ZqQyrgVGZoO_jWdEfo9N7iUWNhWtziPOWpX2qJGxQe4w_6wmIWcUQAPQvvSTg5zd2v3NEm82LW_CYOLSHv-7c3xqxu-aFfri-hOKh3lqqC82sON5LIlg2BzDkYQg==]. The Asia-Pacific rum market was valued at **USD 7.31 billion in 2024** and is expected to grow at a CAGR of **4.1% from 2025 to 2030**, reaching **USD 9.26 billion** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGMuB3Z6p6G9Kn-p7A7zB3Q4r-zYa9APK3SvU1FcE-_nycGhhAhqGMcmlDv7an6Kc9l9iMFx0y2bl4kq6FdXXlhFxx729bVgAOokB6-mlySS-MGnXkeWJgfPwQga3csPtOlyCDMEJtrJNqrG2vo1TmH10CeJ13mbR6CwCPIFYl0RuDR65mXVqvavDVUY6Y=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQED5B23D4tKGV2S8mqKsfwIn2q84MwYRZwVjbi4Cvi13oWMlCXMlFV0t8A30P1wjy7EMGxlEyp-T11j84fj-kaKCSmsMU0w2Hbqi2J-frxrqq-6nEtKCXOndk6s20l8EtXgnXUidJ_y7IsjT0zeBOjupszulKb4VF94-cw7ukDiHEspB2A=]. Another estimate places the Asia-Pacific rum market at **USD 4.30 billion in 2025**, growing to **USD 7.43 billion by 2034** with a CAGR of **6.26%** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHD40eC0Ypyo5qzm01XLEQbEEpJGIodnqnjpiS3FmVOjyxXPlTT35JB7DBWLFfwInR93Td21p96Mkc0q1w31HhVaoFFdoFeBre2Hzi7BHPkXIXhvFF2QCkXGKUAgnM8xru6y5Djm3hlC2Cpg3zPcffod9uDXXit5eZfezoUp4aHAtdkzcs6MlIRJXOcjQBO, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGboTOy3ni7LYw-phqkSf2OIcivt1fHra_7RQippbWR7Amy2wRJkHIDebaZ8NPg34qpBgQW3X7JbXETx9sezzljxXR-zCtDj7CFEMah_R1C7NINZJSn5E80wTo1I00DOAEi7MVjFOaLoSH3OpdbSkittqq2e_uiAQ==]. White rum holds **42.5% of the total volume consumption in APAC in 2025** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGMuB3Z6p6G9Kn-p7A7zB3Q4r-zYa9APK3SvU1FcE-_nycGhhAhqGMcmlDv7an6Kc9l9iMFx0y2bl4kq6FdXXlhFxx729bVgAOokB6-mlySS-MGnXkeWJgfPwQga3csPtOlyCDMEJtrJNqrG2vo1TmH10CeJ13mbR6CwCPIFYl0RuDR65mXVqvavDVUY6Y=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQED5B23D4tKGV2S8mqKsfwIn2q84MwYRZwVjbi4Cvi13oWMlCXMlFV0t8A30P1wjy7EMGxlEyp-T11j84fj-kaKCSmsMU0w2Hbqi2J-frxrqq-6nEtKCXOndk6s20l8EtXgnXUidJ_y7IsjT0zeBOjupszulKb4VF94-cw7ukDiHEspB2A=]. Spiced rum is the fastest-growing segment in APAC, expanding at a CAGR of **10.8%** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGMuB3Z6p6G9Kn-p7A7zB3Q4r-zYa9APK3SvU1FcE-_nycGhhAhqGMcmlDv7an6Kc9l9iMFx0y2bl4kq6FdXXlhFxx729bVgAOokB6-mlySS-MGnXkeWJgfPwQga3csPtOlyCDMEJtrJNqrG2vo1TmH10CeJ13mbR6CwCPIFYl0RuDR65mXVqvavDVUY6Y=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQED5B23D4tKGV2S8mqKsfwIn2q84MwYRZwVjbi4Cvi13oWMlCXMlFV0t8A30P1wjy7EMGxlEyp-T11j84fj-kaKCSmsMU0w2Hbqi2J-frxrqq-6nEtKCXOndk6s20l8EtXgnXUidJ_y7IsjT0zeBOjupszulKb4VF94-cw7ukDiHEspB2A=]. Asia-Pacific held a **39.59% market share in 2024** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHnUDpItc_njSI6WSJ0H4iujRflJAIJbI6-CA4J-PUZZTWSNdNeoKND_WVaOnv9hqkoVaZEfClbfonjg6Iy808QAiH7rcffAn6rKnj_NRxlpYM6KiSUFLBQK0TO7_qwpWapHsEhDrTl10XSTSunejQfghgFT3HPwgHleA=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFhZzgJCNOo75Zf6_DS9AyF7wWBrIvrs3tL8d5j0Iu8bcyspQksrZadmzBxtgXK7ttt3KN8i5nQsTciIN64nNqNJPj6TeijKx4U36g_OWovmTE0poxJ_b9LPtt8wAuCwg5q].\n*   **Latin America & Canada:** Key markets include **Mexico, Canada, Chile, and Argentina** (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/sites/default/files/2023-09/FY23%20Full-Year%20Results%20Presentation.pdf, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2023/09/havana-club-targets-gen-z-with-new-campaign/). **Mexico is emerging as a significant market for Havana Club 7 Años**, potentially becoming the number one or two export market for this expression (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/sites/default/files/2023-09/FY23%20Full-Year%20Results%20Presentation.pdf, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2023/09/havana-club-targets-gen-z-with-new-campaign/).\n*   **Middle East & Africa:** The Middle East & Africa rum market was valued at **USD 0.94 billion in 2025** and is projected to grow at a CAGR of **4.73% from 2026 to 2034**, reaching **USD 1.42 billion** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHD6zAWiDHvxJBF1fXkk84smxQbuF-1U8QPddrK9w1V5-ml_1J31n5Eq1dkbDyDWbTWzRRwrUE5LRe_cR13nMp4l2XtPMrNRA3G_t1o1i3QOP9THOxRm9vIwq-19h-VbT1g8h9dtIwgpfC0LiTKOKNvIfA704Gty11FMuVQb8bp-HuL9Rc=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGboTOy3ni7LYw-phqkSf2OIcivt1fHra_7RQippbWR7Amy2wRJkHIDebaZ8NPg34qpBgQW3X7JbXETx9sezzljxXR-zCtDj7CFEMah_R1C7NINZJSn5E80wTo1I00DOAEi7MVjFOaLoSH3OpdbSkittqq2e_uiAQ==]. South Africa is a key market in MEA, holding **39% of the region's market in 2024**, with its rum market generating **USD 140.6 million in 2024** and expected to reach **USD 177.0 million by 2030**, with a CAGR of **4% from 2025 to 2030** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHD6zAWiDHvxJBF1fXkk84smxQbuF-1U8QPddrK9w1V5-ml_1J31n5Eq1dkbDyDWbTWzRRwrUE5LRe_cR13nMp4l2XtPMrNRA3G_t1o1i3QOP9THOxRm9vIwq-19h-VbT1g8h9dtIwgpfC0LiTKOKNvIfA704Gty11FMuVQb8bp-HuL9Rc=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGboTOy3ni7LYw-phqkSf2OIcivt1fHra_7RQippbWR7Amy2wRJkHIDebaZ8NPg34qpBgQW3X7JbXETx9sezzljxXR-zCtDj7CFEMah_R1C7NINZJSn5E80wTo1I00DOAEi7MVjFOaLoSH3OpdbSkittqq2e_uiAQ==].\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"5. Campaigns","content":"\nHavana Club actively engages in collaborations and global campaigns to drive brand visibility and appeal to its target demographics:\n*   The **'Havana Club x Skepta' collaboration in 2020** resulted in **36,000 limited-edition bottles selling out in just six weeks** (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/media/press-releases/havana-club-x-skepta-collaboration-sells-out-in-six-weeks, https://www.thedrinksbusiness.com/2020/11/havana-club-x-skepta-collaboration-sells-out-in-six-weeks/). This collaboration was part of key initiatives targeting Gen Z consumers [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFZjwIS4j3pL5I5FdgVZ6NCGWJJzCsdNPfKk5y3Rb1EUbvTrPR8pjrQcA1w9MflG7qAsjvt-dPQJkOqMjMV3KOJp0QVoUauJPHSqTy7EFZIP-n8_bwuU6-fDRY-A_a5Fi2NP4NQjkuwmU3GeYcGj0qpbIqI-TNFoOR0qBOxDFW-4cshpHvof4aJUWY-ITE90ru0xK4vb-ZvrAQ=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQETTxpk1vZ-pbuGylgPngUjRyUG5pl4IwowULj6isjdRFXKNeIAebY9Qh0GgUfdwH2tAsV6N2zIzNs7VKBdN6f67J8yQy8ZUIDoGCk72te4f8vebTWEodsOtWIS-M5_QLdeD87eIwu2mictl3qbIN8QHXHkbu1myNN2vdOpiBWzRqmIG7_s047CdaXOhPBL2-vr4QdNCrGthkI9wVr-5Q1TSy_CluM=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHh1Hrhawy0TPf_5dckWQTnbyk0ONdM-miYGIZKyMiHdZvhGtqDNwiGiiVbg8wMvXsxxe2w2ynmeLacQSjt2vGJoGkD94M5L6GoX80x8FwpCyhQhWtGGdRbRc9F2zdo1HGvhBU2rH2ij2wQSyM_zrFk3Q==].\n*   The **'Havana Club x Places+Faces' collaboration in July 2023** contributed to Havana Club growing **+2.9% in value in the off-trade** (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/media/press-releases/havana-club-x-places-faces-collaboration-drives-growth, https://www.just-drinks.com/news/pernod-ricard-reports-strong-havana-club-growth-driven-by-collaborations/). This was also a key initiative targeting Gen Z consumers [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFZjwIS4j3pL5I5FdgVZ6NCGWJJzCsdNPfKk5y3Rb1EUbvTrPR8pjrQcA1w9MflG7qAsjvt-dPQJkOqMjMV3KOJp0QVoUauJPHSqTy7EFZIP-n8_bwuU6-fDRY-A_a5Fi2NP4NQjkuwmU3GeYcGj0qpbIqI-TNFoOR0qBOxDFW-4cshpHvof4aJUWY-ITE90ru0xK4vb-ZvrAQ=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQETTxpk1vZ-pbuGylgPngUjRyUG5pl4IwowULj6isjdRFXKNeIAebY9Qh0GgUfdwH2tAsV6N2zIzNs7VKBdN6f67J8yQy8ZUIDoGCk72te4f8vebTWEodsOtWIS-M5_QLdeD87eIwu2mictl3qbIN8QHXHkbu1myNN2vdOpiBWzRqmIG7_s047CdaXOhPBL2-vr4QdNCrGthkI9wVr-5Q1TSy_CluM=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHh1Hrhawy0TPf_5dckWQTnbyk0ONdM-miYGIZKyMiHdZvhGtqDNwiGiiVbg8wMvXsxxe2w2ynmeLacQSjt2vGJoGkD94M5L6GoX80x8FwpCyhQhWtGGdRbRc9F2zdo1HGvhBU2rH2ij2wQSyM_zrFk3Q==].\n*   Havana Club launched its **'Cuban Mode' global campaign in November 2022**, which rolled out in Canada, Belgium, Germany, Greece, Italy, the Netherlands, and the UK [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEEkPk-1Ka1-uBpOT0Y9YLUKMxmzgI8wA4tR4eZ8ToLODGYB2LcT_XMC647CBvK-iGXhlLVmQ2wB1hLnysbSwATFZyjp8gMp8vQZ8U7_fuyISSFxGvOyBJ1DHzXWE601uRz2-ePgHOlnE5SgNSPKg==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZz6h5k8ik-X2QhJfeK0698SocZEnO0QNxSgPUXUU6QZ-vh4h-53Z_ywlAwsPCV3-mdgAHw3wer52T8A26S58UqKyC_tFbsm6wSou1jF6WFO80dCnWG4Zb03w6vV30KlOcuJp_n1N2w4suU2WEwoM4FlMu54lJI4==]. This campaign is ongoing in **2024-2025** (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/media/press-releases/havana-club-launches-cuban-mode-global-campaign, https://www.thedrinksbusiness.com/2024/03/havana-club-unveils-cuban-mode-campaign/).\n*   The brand launched a **limited-edition Summer 2024 bottle** (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/media/press-releases/havana-club-unveils-summer-2024-limited-edition-bottle, https://www.packagingnews.co.uk/design/havana-club-unveils-summer-2024-limited-edition-bottle).\n*   Havana Club collaborated with goldsmith Jonathan Raksha for a **2024 Añejo 7 Años bottle** (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/media/press-releases/havana-club-x-jonathan-raksha-anejo-7-anos, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2024/05/havana-club-unveils-jonathan-raksha-collaboration/).\n*   Havana Club held the **second edition of the global 'Cocktail Maestros' competition in 2025** (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/media/press-releases/havana-club-cocktail-maestros-2025, https://www.drinksint.com/news/fullstory.php/aid/10987/Havana_Club_announces_Cocktail_Maestros_2025.html).\n*   Havana Club launched a **Cuban Spiced variant in 2021**, targeting millennials and legal-drinking-age Gen Z consumers (https://www.pernod-ricard.com/sites/default/files/2023-09/FY23%20Full-Year%20Results%20Presentation.pdf, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2023/09/havana-club-targets-gen-z-with-new-campaign/). This was also a key initiative targeting Gen Z consumers [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFZjwIS4j3pL5I5FdgVZ6NCGWJJzCsdNPfKk5y3Rb1EUbvTrPR8pjrQcA1w9MflG7qAsjvt-dPQJkOqMjMV3KOJp0QVoUauJPHSqTy7EFZIP-n8_bwuU6-fDRY-A_a5Fi2NP4NQjkuwmU3GeYcGj0qpbIqI-TNFoOR0qBOxDFW-4cshpHvof4aJUWY-ITE90ru0xK4vb-ZvrAQ=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQETTxpk1vZ-pbuGylgPngUjRyUG5pl4IwowULj6isjdRFXKNeIAebY9Qh0GgUfdwH2tAsV6N2zIzNs7VKBdN6f67J8yQy8ZUIDoGCk72te4f8vebTWEodsOtWIS-M5_QLdeD87eIwu2mictl3qbIN8QHXHkbu1myNN2vdOpiBWzRqmIG7_s047CdaXOhPBL2-vr4QdNCrGthkI9wVr-5Q1TSy_CluM=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHh1Hrhawy0TPf_5dckWQTnbyk0ONdM-miYGIZKyMiHdZvhGtqDNwiGiiVbg8wMvXsxxe2w2ynmeLacQSjt2vGJoGkD94M5L6GoX80x8FwpCyhQhWtGGdRbRc9F2zdo1HGvhBU2rH2ij2wQSyM_zrFk3Q==].\n*   Havana Club evolved its **Ready-to-Drink (RTD) range design in August 2024** to unify its global presence and prepare for future expansion, with specific plans for dynamic markets like Germany [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHMradEI_Mjkcem8fgvsWMqxbrW0DpOmE2BlVtobeAnnbY0QQW7nz8mVih1I98nmS5tQfHl1I2O804kQa_vXqHCpzXETvZ9t2tRYq-SS_hcYGCNNSqqqHIPWGRUDXs0gGDgZBrj_xrn743uUp77oMELqJRfBjh4jp1X7cj6ZohS, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQENU_bNlVQunvaYSl2zj5i_DWT]. In **February 2026**, Havana Club is set to launch a Havana Club Spezi RTD in Germany, demonstrating a tailored market approach [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEDnaV0ANBEDzhOGIqaggddn_DIG7K2LR2yqLR2oM7ERPpq8ELLK76_xsppRh3r05JmP_02oDDKVuPx59_kyysGOhcL6CexyrpcedYStJidMWw1oLRP5xZ_tK2J52B1isodzlTLvjXIzLcDpy4u7HZ1GO0zOYigTFvNaF20LSF5XPwbYaj4kg==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFBFtqbL8vzCnmEYvXTaVP_iDmqpxtI7NZlv0EEIuUOrFhUkfcUkxOGMf3aUKdjbit30LJQ-QnH64UXAC3U-gN7j_Z1-6tkb3HwTCYuusSw79IVnk8B0S36MkJMEWR7-DJ6DOqCCccBZrTWsquywy0EpCwFU_uHgPKYYa47WTZZdr1a7CuvvXiAfBSIw6qodfNAc8P734ho-BjzP8z5XlI_GXm07R_1Jp2jXFXgWg==].\n*   Havana Club partnered with British menswear designer Martine Rose for a limited-edition Añejo 7 Años bottle in **November 2025** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGkRQW1kLA5i5EsgnC4K6dTNMDzxgzbK_ccO9HRSCNKVP4XTmTMSKg2hl-XyFBMObDneYZVLFAy8iduZdAqvaipTEj2y6UP_5wiWL4Ywa37Y2q4CbYux3FR6ycE1FZPDryaGtPUqh5WdQ5R6JpPAncLEn6b6UBhdzwqga7TqUhGZcwTpiTUlxqKChFI28g=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZz6h5k8ik-X2QhJfeK0698SocZEnO0QNxSgPUXUU6QZ-vh4h-53Z_ywlAwsPCV3-mdgAHw3wer52T8A26S58UqKyC_tFbsm6wSou1jF6WFO80dCnWG4Zb03w6vV30KlOcuJp_n1N2w4suU2WEwoM4FlMu54lJI4==].\n*   Havana Club implemented a closed-loop distribution system with EcoSpirits in Cuba in **July 2024**, aiming to reduce carbon emissions by **88%** and glass waste by **99%** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEH4PexyTpOupx3YnVOWSy0Rde2YF8lb3X_2PWmR4bjUWcqGKHlrrF3qle1s3oC-2NVcZBnbVgbaO7Kg8rmgImioYqrfXilFQQ-bp7aZIcN5fiqYUT5NXtK9DiBQXsTqybtLfbOooFUQf5vogulAPvhay5z1fwHp7_D8UekYhK7GO3SkdQ0U5eWSky6gT1ry216K5XBMjs3FwpAKcHkqhQq_tGauPzI6gKchtY5ymUXIrmTDsaFm88iIeOt8f1Mw2fKpLVXtE2k0wcWsMspYW9HKV_eJ8LqJb5S8_7l-9s==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFPb5JEoVtI-Li4WLc0E7TYbPudyxuZQ3YP64jBAaf7sAyH75Dg7pJUtJZiyoMHHFzKxJbbLtvlt1sJfZHyoX4aG_rnzo0qdlo7VBV5oZ3BRjzGEWyLFihtw0aKY-1TOJfBU93H_ycClaHldfsyefI7hDKCjkCEiva4mUgnffy60Wyt0H51V412z-doP4=]. This initiative, launched in **January 2024**, reduced **10 tons of waste and 16 tons of CO2 emissions in 2024** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQETlhErkegJH9Y7i_bs3K4LfejZSGd8D-3VNw5xH16zgTIKc4-nLIro2kaKEm-Kmabt2wb3hJqNDSCloJGH8msdrlSGmL1Sbqy-NZPhRHTf4KQllCBL3_N2J20nZUtXmMOWmW_J, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHIsfCipXojLckt2vY8wRi7Gi2Em6ImsJ7j-8y-2uoSCnkYg8BPmgh45cJOXSORSLSgPXIAou0orvP4q0exH9HErcBANJ9o_O_KAWvNMfz2Q8DUrixGuQUhRyIe785d_978KzBrTwq7e5EUmiWbu-HQ5XMDxZP2_dE8hKVvVeruI6Wv8rmLyvePZETVdCbIcTnt].\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"6. Current Strategy","content":"\nHavana Club's current strategy, as evidenced by its recent campaigns and target market shift, is heavily focused on:\n*   **Premiumization:** Emphasizing aged expressions for neat/on-the-rocks consumption and launching high-value limited editions (e.g., Tributo 2025 at €450). Havana Club's CEO Christian Barré emphasized premiumization as a 'very important strategic pillar' for the brand in **December 2023** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFZwhZhNWFpsDXjVeGghkO3Xf42Nxx3JEdun5Rii9FUaLqdMb18xwm2jlM2l578w7QiLmNcOil4bDSMYuYhYapfWlH7LneSerAU2rbMkJzFo_3ayEnOaCZlyLFj3_OdUxUCfvPn4GTBOE8ERa4muVAb9p3ns0w=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEtJ7HglfyHgdtY8QfupFhSa-Qv06P614y2C_uPO4RDEn6bv6sytheHGKC-OqGhXRSy5jAfOiIoNyAYD3YROKp8wNti2EFh0dqbpKaLUy43cSqJATxJTppXzOg3EHKJYgVjDi8XLx-902gysrlNxUupWmPrj7JjOyvZfj8fDeeGIBgQPQXDnx_Jy1DRrNfCNgeHB12zIz8b3b-JhYhj9dsbJ7pk6Zi2YzwJTSTwWsRSVo0=\"]. The super-premium and above rum segment is projected to grow at an **8% CAGR between 2024 and 2028** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGQp--XfcvFLJvx-lY5xBDUpL1SRmmdeHTDKqCMltBo0iSxSWQRW0xIHIInM1en3o066A7n-wmWndsYNmT9ivUq0iMNmxzZutyRKnKL_lVLUEV35CkqUfW7IzJbVJzbYkZ5aJurWuMCbGB9-5bwMuHpIDPshJm5uA7qszN2LYjbB2n9gMRMB_Tc, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEV8IEPECHldDfjDXAx3YsdkacdiZquFAvPQ0onYqdLmhif9dVZ0PHX5S-H-kuE14XInyONZN0fs8GYS90ovIBhl6ksSQ2IIeKZKMf609UKFgjiJKL7_BOy0RtOJGQWjH95aR2sXWbifRhe3cmGl___JplbofbHfxPXhCZMBg-xVTklNj9UfSr7mDg58aZIx1tR]. The global premium rum market had a retail value of **$2.5 billion in 2022** and is projected to grow at a **5.1% Compound Annual Growth Rate (CAGR) until 2027** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGEDi0Zg0MUHD-_3KcJmwcd4p80gOe6CoVhG8Yqj0bzaaZL5mnXuGAU8xJYKQ2LS3uQOwuzbdtUlNAEEIGBooQebvffFDYJhoZPm1_cTwaRwAy2t2HpZCjzAO6aq4xmcD-D6Kx6uE9bv0IHINgZlPjKsoF55m0UNGvUMgZO, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEL5h9XxePjVkJE_sdye5Vl9e0iZ9o1NmeQVmIWkSa3cQav8iXRuvZhTgI-f5qkK1pUFjNZPcatqBDHphPfqSqqJku99Jsd66jg4saNHEHhtpkos3mJbXUyghsYZHtbHoc8jUwVWIaDFZd5rTEidCjDLdk=]. The global super-premium-and-above rum segment is projected to grow at a CAGR of **6% between 2022 and 2027**, following a **10% increase in 2022** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHWrD2zeNVTehls4vN4l0M27qGopsI9syfGnOSfTH_0Ym-smejMglq6KDSAhhVCIJHjJ1LHFnQQeXiu3IPNpl2eeVhZPuhhnBbOjvhseUwaaZgbZEEkVthWpRRr9BJe, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHEbMofEGmJGcwsR-_SaeI4QV-jEaxKIEr5y01cBMVUhNsNnap-XGMTGhOrKfSvxibb5r896TMTshTqCKD5htqrRGGIG90VioPo52hBTvRuxV81VgisvRKfhh49QT6FSo9s0C4_k2PEOAkaFMQDgXFtMUl8J9cjZRc_dQr8QGJkIBoZeVU=].\n*   **Youth Engagement (Gen Z):** Shifting focus to a \"streetwear-inspired\" Gen Z cohort, utilizing collaborations with relevant cultural figures and brands (Skepta, Places+Faces, Martine Rose). Gen Z accounts for approximately **25% of Pernod Ricard's digital engagement** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG7xAZ76ll83by8-F6PMpXq5fSalMUOQRs7imN7pAKKP0FXuG_gn08NpdScJmommJ12EcM7Qa7l73IKPoNiS3nnT_HyucTC_rqWZwtCvnRRn2hgCWJlsvzTMII6O_EMqGmB0DUJp3gJaH4ysQ1cBBa7JScUwivdnKpGADwzRJmbWZ8-C9a2ni5iLGonMMhJsQc4CZYUtTFSn4_C8BomMVuQ4Op6Z-K3ZLzr3dcCTyEL, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHQxfDuNh6nvd_RJRPOusRhqBm-NzI25HiyvbFX_2NQlLJMr9Rq1t2glHnAMjz4mvj_cGzvqPWkFkUodONfSA2vKE5kIOYnOOPlBZPdXYd29NEMLIvVZPrcGjDe7QVlFzbuFf1YAZ5u67Uqn02vNZuB3mu-Ge_2Xek=\"].\n*   **Global Expansion:** Targeting emerging markets like India and China with a premium offering, while strengthening presence in key European and Latin American markets.\n*   **Digital & Cultural Relevance:** Leveraging collaborations and campaigns to maintain brand visibility and appeal in contemporary culture. Competitors like Brugal and Captain Morgan have launched immersive digital campaigns and social media engagements [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGIOveGrfNEABnVyen56UgElaBVXpKUrh_9-cWtiw2Rzlaz8OKiPt6XGmooNoMEqT4mpxmqX5DJbGpGODLivRtY8wCWK4kZxUJsdWLy2nLMjTU6NhNmEWwG-2kdYlaV2kv8liSiGlrpKzutZoEKLA-MlRqPE65hic13CFtYWvz7j8wJyn50RkWmdY5QiWATOAGkr_PkqhOGSaNablbOA==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGxbYzRyz7tzrq7oPTzEUEOpBIweB9X4yJIb-74edH03vopRPw8zlkCWOij10Gvbs-c6HlTDQDMVO8sM23g62h3FlScfKbJxXfr_bRUKQza0pOeH0xqQee4k9vrIpBNBpvoZhimcb7F7I-qe-qtzHGDTPiovibL3HE3kNoNx681JH-GUhZrsXs3Q3cwa54==]. Pernod Ricard allocates over **75% of its paid media efforts to digital channels** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG7xAZ76ll83by8-F6PMpXq5fSalMUOQRs7imN7pAKKP0FXuG_gn08NpdScJmommJ12EcM7Qa7l73IKPoNiS3nnT_HyucTC_rqWZwtCvnRRn2hgCWJlsvzTMII6O_EMqGmB0DUJp3gJaH4ysQ1cBBa7JScUwivdnKpGADwzRJmbWZ8-C9a2ni5iLGonMMhJsQc4CZYUtTFSn4_C8BomMVuQ4Op6Z-K3ZLzr3dcCTyEL, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHQxfDuNh6nvd_RJRPOusRhqBm-NzI25HiyvbFX_2NQlLJMr9Rq1t2glHnAMjz4mvj_cGzvqPWkFkUodONfSA2vKE5kIOYnOOPlBZPdXYd29NEMLIvVZPrcGjDe7QVlFzbuFf1YAZ5u67Uqn02vNZuB3mu-Ge_2Xek=\"].\n*   **Authenticity & Provenance:** Continuously highlighting its Cuban origin and traditional rum-making, reinforced by the UNESCO recognition.\n*   **Cocktail Culture:** Maintaining a strong presence in bars and promoting its use in cocktails through initiatives like 'Cocktail Maestros'.\n*   **Ready-to-Drink (RTD) Development:** Havana Club has evolved its RTD range design in August 2024 to unify its global presence and prepare for future expansion, with specific plans for dynamic markets like Germany [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHMradEI_Mjkcem8fgvsWMqxbrW0DpOmE2BlVtobeAnnbY0QQW7nz8mVih1I98nmS5tQfHl1I2O804kQa_vXqHCpzXETvZ9t2tRYq-SS_hcYGCNNSqqqHIPWGRUDXs0gGDgZBrj_xrn743uUp77oMELqJRfBjh4jp1X7cj6ZohS, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQENU_bNlVQunvaYSl2zj5i_DWT]. Pernod Ricard USA also established a dedicated RTD division in May 2025 with plans to triple its U.S. RTD footprint over the next three years, including new distribution partnerships [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE_-MozeM_ga4seAWPVItYX_QMfahwOXtSADeVagxWJmNphCn29qmHwpY3talUx4HOhZFsTu7C9CGs-6vIqsnyLNGmG1ywBFAGnjDLXiiCB28uxdGXVvMHin-22kt94vAXMgjrYhFntPOqfBZ-le7N4o9FXW-LBCUHV5qPXUDQX9OvhpudGb_e6p1PDaqqQlJkXj75UqNoqWxqFyw==\", https://vertexaisearch.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEBy4NsPdItu6JXQ3GLKlrIbuv4rPiKzho_UBN-INoL2bk-KU88ewA4cPopnPI0lwkav1Z2FHdy8QAEzcnsz8Y_N1C16-qSW8Sr2XxZ4aBNOPRBFNg6_bjaMoj2mztfrHfsHuYMKggxgEWg48_uQKZ2O1kCUaoibk65UFJGns4pC3CA0D641Tdxj_ZznzRgQ5TDzp4cH3auTonUI-fypT2PRU=\"]. Pernod Ricard established a dedicated RTD division in **2025** and identified Havana Club as a 'clear choice' for RTD development [https://www.pernod-ricard.com/en/media/pernod-ricard-usa-unveils-major-transformation-its-route-market-strategy, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2025/01/pernod-ricard-usa-overhauls-route-to-market/]. Pernod Ricard aims for RTDs to contribute **10-15% to the Group's total sales growth** over the next five years [https://www.pernod-ricard.com/en/media/press-releases/pernod-ricard-accelerates-rtd-strategy, https://www.just-drinks.com/news/pernod-ricard-targets-rtds-for-10-15-of-sales-growth/]. Havana Club's current RTD product portfolio includes **Havana Club Cuban Spiced mixed with cola (launched 2021)** [https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2021/04/havana-club-launches-cuban-spiced-rtd/, https://www.pernod-ricard.com/en/brands/havana-club] and **Havana Club Verde & Tonic RTD (launched in Germany in 2022)** [https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2022/07/havana-club-verde-gets-rtd-format/, https://www.pernod-ricard.com/en/brands/havana-club]. Havana Club holds a **leadership position in rum RTDs in Germany** [https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2022/07/havana-club-verde-gets-rtd-format/], further supported by Pernod Ricard's leading market share by volume in the overall German rum market in 2022 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHYOvluHUNNRKCDejheC_k37kaUoGnriusKOoyTx4SpblMSgvMSuOMFzHnPWp_PG86n92Smm_2WaSUpMn1yLB3FzxCUh0rbENMcIyiX1xYhZPy3iL_iIo6BPMI9OruKYd6r8ldqHD2B19NuCEXTio1e-u39sV89jcfn, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGYCsYz4bDeXVEBO67tBYiUZtCLme8ZAdPrtIVAeqCoHJOZu_hIkBy3QtKY7XhULzNMBcOannYCC8zQhLDfMr4F8XnHP0Glp7bDTmghXSCQPJQlJTN3eJAG_T3XMYiFjM6R6c4cvLpyhvzMD7CbzI-PbHm3b9KfQrCfNv4uw8wJJsSGrn2AnM7uwe_1MGB9KIBbn6HwKwWbkUrQskG_TT6pWtENvhOo]. The global RTD alcoholic beverage market was valued at **USD 40.2 billion in 2025** and is projected to reach **USD 79.6 billion by 2034**, growing at a CAGR of **7.9% from 2026 to 2034** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHTG9A1dwGJhpAGcjSL4ONVgyDZ8X112EPZ7NE4WmiwywiDPUt_9fP_ZvOQyp5xVjgDTSkJMiDfxdHdqgzw5yDfn0gwL5iN5VF1hEUXfflTZGQvPlZVc16PNw3Y8Qj5_hOJNjoV8z7230UPWKZKfMD7__YFKJVkx9y9scxHiq3KubyfzE-g==\", https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEAauUJcNsNcKnXRVADZjRurv-NE5yCSXLrnl3-mulfM5VXjowVW22_fcw8DW0wrZRkGzXW5rq6no9MaDchrCyhJ3I5o6BM-8Is1isiEN0pXRBEbg_iwzR8dqQAZ6seXgXGlPGMLWk0M5Jgu3Si7V69hD13s3y-yL1eEPMS8Q==\"]. The global RTD cocktails market, a key sub-segment, was valued at **USD 3.76 billion in 2025** and is projected to reach **USD 13.86 billion by 2034**, with a CAGR of **15.59% from 2026 to 2034** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFv-z7RZolp8jlLEP1UU7TyikPyCsgLPTxNUf7wOhcRTXKEooBUd2rLAYcRpKerLAPFZv5l86Kth2IxO58sN0zn0U_LGrWLkjcTOVrJKG0LZ0GNFrVhkWPyLiWfevbnFl4C7YpO-8BiwBj6fNjqAUHKyx0o7ZhT3aMkknJqeSs=\", https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEKQA6MWRhI3JCnRH1oXa-ZLETX5FVRpslFUFFjh98A8ZhzkzsUOX6OQsjraLRZM2W-gX3a4G74XrZ7h3sEidTwD8q9nZ8pRP44A_yRGFgQj1xr2Acid1YBSahiFkUp3cAZ7lqWthZGmL2Vn8OFlAdo_uTiq_fPLIuMhywDk9looh7frQ].\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"7. Performance","content":"\nHavana Club demonstrates a mixed but strategically positive performance, driven by premiumization efforts:\n*   **International Value Growth (FY24):** Havana Club achieved an **8% growth in value internationally** between July 2023 and June 2024 (FY24) (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9YJlMJnKOnsPunUJIKTMp4pjm2MLCz1e6k4m1CtJoIF-L5T7O6IG76CmNymhSiSV_yvo5LiuwA6LJV8DOzsvMTc87qkqLYcKf6P2CeYo9jWWq3Es8WIIelM0eNWaIM5gku6B_MLpLRAXr57JXjwarV-kTwCsQGjOFpk8E72i3ryhJ0eMdTjCKeLU1SF2glkz6inRYSB7fDHwTzxe3DPz, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHatGq9zUHbd-wlNefvLyhL7qmODSlFZEGuldqiZ4G-Bzts8V6aeGvhX2zs_AdurP07D7gEZB4oenok8-HXWdSD9pu7if7grVjQ5bBuFKrSjNJc2Syx1e0dicXrWfft3f9XYL4OYn63q6a4fZGiuTzYjZQtPHw) [https://www.pernod-ricard.com/sites/default/files/2024-08/Pernod%20Ricard%20FY24%20Results%20Presentation.pdf, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2024/08/pernod-ricard-reports-strong-fy24-results/]. Havana Club's international sales increased by **8.0% between July 2023 and June 2024** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGHWVG09YZ6pYZGjS68A1-9cr19hf7H8TpQHBZmC1wzkuN31bNAHtdqXi4SPv400fyuktYgEo3ZMpUvyiv7tlPvtdCpH1eVYosZVd4ApB9phN5ivJ5TIspUGCK8AKVnux7Vk7U6xpk9XBsG05p-FRlWb3egWdeCQXWl7pAB_mNQa_nqBA5XLFLlkLoSVQXx8xGxrh8JZooUqIQJuDvltzCD, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEnO6g71syuFpcPVBhz9J5NKwnK4nFKBtbdmnqaKt1c1DI2v_9TMAL4eutp2tdBY9fhWo5eWarcX2OMzaEtDLZzfxsjHI_8c2ESLYXRTSFsXzVX6yeGWGh5J0bx6Su2gIfhiKY2dafFCLUVDp4c2kKlRAW8ef8zCflxPbq50Y_ZfQHl-2lg-KyEXiM=\"].\n*   **Value Growth in Cuba (FY24):** The brand achieved a significant **55% value growth in Cuba** between July 2023 and June 2024 (FY24) (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9YJlMJnKOnsPunUJIKTMp4pjm2MLCz1e6k4m1CtJoIF-L5T7O6IG76CmNymhSiSV_yvo5LiuwA6LJV8DOzsvMTc87qkqLYcKf6P2CeYo9jWWq3Es8WIIelM0eNWaIM5gku6B_MLpLRAXr57JXjwarV-kTwCsQGjOFpk8E72i3ryhJ0eMdTjCKeLU1SF2glkz6inRYSB7fDHwTzxe3DPz, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHatGq9zUHbd-wlNefvLyhL7qmODSlFZEGuldqiZ4G-Bzts8V6aeGvhX2zs_AdurP07D7gEZB4oenok8-HXWdSD9pu7if7grVjQ5bBuFKrSjNJc2Syx1e0dicXrWfft3f9XYL4OYn63q6a4fZGiuTzYjZQtPHw). Havana Club's value grew by **55% between July 2023 and June 2024**, primarily driven by higher-value, aged products [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGHWVG09YZ6pYZGjS68A1-9cr19hf7H8TpQHBZmC1wzkuN31bNAHtdqXi4SPv400fyuktYgEo3ZMpUvyiv7tlPvtdCpH1eVYosZVd4ApB9phN5ivJ5TIspUGCK8AKVnux7Vk7U6xpk9XBsG05p-FRlWb3egWdeCQXWl7pAB_mNQa_nqBA5XLFLlkLoSVQXx8xGxrh8JZooUqIQJuDvltzCD, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEnO6g71syuFpcPVBhz9J5NKwnK4nFKBtbdmnqaKt1c1DI2v_9TMAL4eutp2tdBY9fhWo5eWarcX2OMzaEtDLZzfxsjHI_8c2ESLYXRTSFsXzVX6yeGWGh5J0bx6Su2gIfhiKY2dafFCLUVDp4c2kKlRAW8ef8zCflxPbq50Y_ZfQHl-2lg-KyEXiM=\"].\n*   **Global Sales Volume (FY23):** Havana Club sold **4.3 million 9-liter cases globally** in fiscal year 2023 (ending June 2023) (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9YJlMJnKOnsPunUJIKTMp4pjm2MLCz1e6k4m1CtJoIF-L5T7O6IG76CmNymhSiSV_yvo5LiuwA6LJV8DOzsvMTc87qkqLYcKf6P2CeYo9jWWq3Es8WIIelM0eNWaIM5gku6B_MLpLRAXr57JXjwarV-kTwCsQGjOFpk8E72i3ryhJ0eMdTjCKeLU1SF2glkz6inRYSB7fDHwTzxe3DPz, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHatGq9zUHbd-wlNefvLyhL7qmODSlFZEGuldqiZ4G-Bzts8V6aeGvhX2zs_AdurP07D7gEZB4oenok8-HXWdSD9pu7if7grVjQ5bBuFKrSjNJc2Syx1e0dicXrWfft3f9XYL4OYn63q6a4fZGiuTzYjZQtPHw). Havana Club's volume was **4.6 million 9-liter cases in 2022** and **3.8 million 9-liter cases in 2023** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGkRQW1kLA5i5EsgnC4K6dTNMDzxgzbK_ccO9HRSCNKVP4XTmTMSKg2hl-XyFBMObDneYZVLFAy8iduZdAqvaipTEj2y6UP_5wiWL4Ywa37Y2q4CbYux3FR6ycE1FZPDryaGtPUqh5WdQ5R6JpPAncLEn6b6UBhdzwqga7TqUhGZcwTpiTUlxqKChFI28g=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGFjDY8IZMEHuzxNqKYlqdfXiWnEwKADDMQupPcv3PZSPO7ckCYGohKhwMrkzh34mPBuu-olJSGpCXSlIVwp3Iv1FSr_ZKRtotQ8Z5NZCP3nAgw-AEKE74eKliCvEcY4QSV7UKrsvmwsswRHQzbCevWlyh9q0fpkd0=]. This represents a **-15.8% change in volume** compared to 2022 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGkRQW1kLA5i5EsgnC4K6dTNMDzxgzbK_ccO9HRSCNKVP4XTmTMSKg2hl-XyFBMObDneYZVLFAy8iduZdAqvaipTEj2y6UP_5wiWL4Ywa37Y2q4CbYux3FR6ycE1FZPDryaGtPUqh5WdQ5R6JpPAncLEn6b6UBhdzwqga7TqUhGZcwTpiTUlxqKChFI28g=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGFjDY8IZMEHuzxNqKYlqdfXiWnEwKADDMQupPcv3PZSPO7ckCYGohKhwMrkzh34mPBuu-olJSGpCXSlIVwp3Iv1FSr_ZKRtotQ8Z5NZCP3nAgw-AEKE74eKliCvEcY4QSV7UKrsvmwsswRHQzbCevWlyh9q0fpkd0=].\n*   **Overall Value Growth (FY23):** The brand experienced a **6% increase in value** in fiscal year 2023 (ending June 2023) (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9YJlMJnKOnsPunUJIKTMp4pjm2MLCz1e6k4m1CtJoIF-L5T7O6IG76CmNymhSiSV_yvo5LiuwA6LJV8DOzsvMTc87qkqLYcKf6P2CeYo9jWWq3Es8WIIelM0eNWaIM5gku6B_MLpLRAXr57JXjwarV-kTwCsQGjOFpk8E72i3ryhJ0eMdTjCKeLU1SF2glkz6inRYSB7fDHwTzxe3DPz, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHatGq9zUHbd-wlNefvLyhL7qmODSlFZEGuldqiZ4G-Bzts8V6aeGvhX2zs_AdurP07D7gEZB4oenok8-HXWdSD9pu7if7grVjQ5bBuFKrSjNJc2Syx1e0dicXrWfft3f9XYL4OYn63q6a4fZGiuTzYjZQtPHw). Havana Club celebrated **6% growth in its 2022/23 full-year financial results** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHHmb0xBreKbGnAF9cJjh2QbsDF4545muSf8t-Ax71jevGQAPG03X26KjqVm6_-7y6-yGmi5X0DerIqpx4wiE-HZT_w7f9Jzi1cPdq7-_iySVvkf7IMhPwhamYQdXp2C73uiYblKK2swe5meThld7OvdUfVPz8H5_4QlN_RtI6Uy-zE5-dUIF2M5_1V8rJCN40lOwQ=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHyUFbTgTPa-CkjtcNQJrPrmaHAr5CzjzS5aXcnKdOjkC8ztKINyGaPyfn8he97Be62It1bekMZaMSk9ImdaKkBKEjaq_nggHXBe3zI1ft4Zir6aRyj48J7D6QoWtWi4XBVptZUmR7WmhasGFTmL3aH3f11sNE_8ug=\"].\n*   **Market Share in Cuba:** Havana Club's market share in Cuba was **60% as of 2023** (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9YJlMJnKOnsPunUJIKTMp4pjm2MLCz1e6k4m1CtJoIF-L5T7O6IG76CmNymhSiSV_yvo5LiuwA6LJV8DOzsvMTc87qkqLYcKf6P2CeYo9jWWq3Es8WIIelM0eNWaIM5gku6B_MLpLRAXr57JXjwarV-kTwCsQGjOFpk8E72i3ryhJ0eMdTjCKeLU1SF2glkz6inRYSB7fDHwTzxe3DPz, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHatGq9zUHbd-wlNefvLyhL7qmODSlFZEGuldqiZ4G-Bzts8V6aeGvhX2zs_AdurP07D7gEZB4oenok8-HXWdSD9pu7if7grVjQ5bBuFKrSjNJc2Syx1e0dicXrWfft3f9XYL4OYn63q6a4fZGiuTzYjZQtPHw).\n*   **Volume vs. Value (Conflicting Data):** Havana Club experienced a **13.8% decrease in cases purchased in calendar year 2024**, according to The Spirits Business Brand Champions Report (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9YJlMJnKOnsPunUJIKTMp4pjm2MLCz1e6k4m1CtJoIF-L5T7O6IG76CmNymhSiSV_yvo5LiuwA6LJV8DOzsvMTc87qkqLYcKf6P2CeYo9jWWq3Es8WIIelM0eNWaIM5gku6B_MLpLRAXr57JXjwarV-kTwCsQGjOFpk8E72i3ryhJ0eMdTjCKeLU1SF2glkz6inRYSB7fDHwTzxe3DPz, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHatGq9zUHbd-wlNefvLyhL7qmODSlFZEGuldqiZ4G-Bzts8V6aeGvhX2zs_AdurP07D7gEZB4oenok8-HXWdSD9pu7if7grVjQ5bBuFKrSjNJc2Syx1e0dicXrWfft3f9XYL4OYn63q6a4fZGiuTzYjZQtPHw). This conflicts with the **55% value growth** in Cuba and **8% international value growth** for FY24. This divergence suggests a strong strategic shift towards premiumization, where higher prices per unit drive value growth despite a reduction in overall volume. The range of performance is from **-13.8% (volume) to +55% (value)**. Havana Club's volume declined from **4.6 million 9-liter cases in 2022 to 3.3 million in 2024** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGIOveGrfNEABnVyen56UgElaBVXpKUrh_9-cWtiw2Rzlaz8OKiPt6XGmooNoMEqT4mpxmqX5DJbGpGODLivRtY8wCWK4kZxUJsdWLy2nLMjTU6NhNmEWwG-2kdYlaV2kv8liSiGlrpKzutZoEKLA-MlRqPE65hic13CFtYWvz7j8wJyn50RkWmdY5QiWATOAGkr_PkqhOGSaNablbOA==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGxbYzRyz7tzrq7oPTzEUEOpBIweB9X4yJIb-74edH03vopRPw8zlkCWOij10Gvbs-c6HlTDQDMVO8sM23g62h3FlScfKbJxXfr_bRUKQza0pOeH0xqQee4k9vrIpBNBpvoZhimcb7F7I-qe-qtzHGDTPiovibL3HE3kNoNx681JH-GUhZrsXs3Q3cwa54==]. The average selling price (ASP) for Havana Club's aged expressions (seven years or more) typically ranges from **USD 40-200 per bottle** [https://www.wine-searcher.com/regions-havana-club, https://www.totalwine.com/spirits/rum/c/000080?viewall=true&pageS]. Havana Club also experienced a **45% decrease in nine-liter box billing volume from July 2023 to June 2024** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEIcDBmtxSs5OCILIRK0If37-IdBh84G1SFrkjfxe5RfucKfiXQABZquvRGA4xVDPz4fDuGtv1SyHNTf9hLqGwFh3guVaU9LENVg5gDDb3qw34_4acXCizQTT5jWzJnKObYiffHIoeRJY4sQa7dPuTfA=, https://vertexaisearch.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGH0ge6nWNtCzcvDtPRyRKK_81DIxjHsLMifvxbxDqKCgA488MplN3Q1O5GgZRgytOjKBxKaJkVrqXN1FLKkKhst7DjYfRcMXW6kJrlkqhl4o44bUjNmbv-g5j4kc4sKI-jM7_J5bzxaD-Xhod3jfNNuKSakUX_Um2aXCYWj-cb2jh__ZFEnk-NVPFBzlDZ9RryRFA=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQElprt-dHekya_M3njIZA4JcY71wXdfZra9wktvyTJZcqOIv-ZSt7fDYdSkFcKXInA04bDBQn2K15AXzOzdzNLPYy7iKVrLuZZ9dFdzJ_B6Zb9Ql2aZcrlKo2o0b3d7HKVVNBU8pLe_1NEdHlpJG3rVIc3ldUlGgaI41lz4RNasW3E_7zdT2QGN4cCI7qWtwQkudkg=]. Havana Club's sales volume declined from **4.6 million 9-liter cases in 2022 to 3.3 million in 2024**, while registering **55% value growth between July 2023 and June 2024** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEyxg3No1UDjE4bwo17zS1-kRBj44-GkB5vPhWB4ZzXlWIj3bABMDcjjnLSIQ5whC1A_BzURxlReMBNWhGj1JRKriowY9hKu3OrzBVtPm_45PnQDdoMX_abG5lsJhZIzw8N7IzvhHMSP6P3o3ab3dikKHvWCEUMNS-YgSmtna2MhLwG6BL8MZMMtrN7hXOpnXgRbQ==\", https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF0p_jpPjiO9xL4t6BtpeBA_5EqsV1p3yDQRqz-EhkQJo2eX7Yojq-CSEi9E1Rcn26H44FTM-o2lNtqXXAx7m-_zPaGkjyP_KnDCnToYkLEsXRVYghs4aVy9ifVxkjiYY9lgZHgZlKWiP2z9vYqlLkN7Zd5fxCI5J8KrrW9QC2uGjOThJ8c2WEtifGrMfo2sNBWHDG1bmw5UJp_cJZwdTs19fziR3wDcBw==\"].\n*   **Global Bottles Sold (2024):** Havana Club sold approximately **45 million bottles worldwide in 2024** (approx. 3.75 million 9L cases) (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9YJlMJnKOnsPunUJIKTMp4pjm2MLCz1e6k4m1CtJoIF-L5T7O6IG76CmNymhSiSV_yvo5LiuwA6LJV8DOzsvMTc87qkqLYcKf6P2CeYo9jWWq3Es8WIIelM0eNWaIM5gku6B_MLpLRAXr57JXjwarV-kTwCsQGjOFpk8E72i3ryhJ0eMdTjCKeLU1SF2glkz6inRYSB7fDHwTzxe3DPz, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHatGq9zUHbd-wlNefvLyhL7qmODSlFZEGuldqiZ4G-Bzts8V6aeGvhX2zs_AdurP07D7gEZB4oenok8-HXWdSD9pu7if7grVjQ5bBuFKrSjNJc2Syx1e0dicXrWfft3f9XYL4OYn63q6a4fZGiuTzYjZQtPHw). Havana Club's volume sales in 2024 totaled **3.3 million 9-liter cases** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHXCdtR2mcwt_D14pA-_9c_MAWooTUdCzyr3u5IqwCJee7N-9I11vQtJw32O_Uwaa2YetIVVJPnhgoH7yekcip1DaQAH1O7uzlO3XdzopIncWMYC7oelgcc_TrwlrPxLYQeSjfmjmifLJ7rXkNwNvXoR19ByBpVazHqQ==\", https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGhlwLErzZo1-cS8a393lA7VytNRyvAflfx10qut4KB3SMyHQWPGnhq5qHDCsU-bYa4s8W51lAnhlE4aSo88CmEp4Ei3ulSQs8WDzoDc38uTghLkM6KGExBN3ut3bSVO2Nv2Sm3kOi40gULOivtntRZtqxGwnioFxqCYwGwEbqp1ABk9SdriYljQSK2IZyCPpbr2uL7oy8om2d1ytQi5w==].\n*   **Global Ranking:** Havana Club is the **third-largest international rum brand globally** (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9YJlMJnKOnsPunUJIKTMp4pjm2MLCz1e6k4m1CtJoIF-L5T7O6IG76CmNymhSiSV_yvo5LiuwA6LJV8DOzsvMTc87qkqLYcKf6P2CeYo9jWWq3Es8WIIelM0eNWaIM5gku6B_MLpLRAXr57JXjwarV-kTwCsQGjOFpk8E72i3ryhJ0eMdTjCKeLU1SF2glkz6inRYSB7fDHwTzxe3DPz, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHatGq9zUHbd-wlNefvLyhL7qmODSlFZEGuldqiZ4G-Bzts8V6aeGvhX2zs_AdurP07D7gEZB4oenok8-HXWdSD9pu7if7grVjQ5bBuFKrSjNJc2Syx1e0dicXrWfft3f9XYL4OYn63q6a4fZGiuTzYjZQtPHw) and the **worldwide leader in super-premium and above rums** (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9YJlMJnKOnsPunUJIKTMp4pjm2MLCz1e6k4m1CtJoIF-L5T7O6IG76CmNymhSiSV_yvo5LiuwA6LJV8DOzsvMTc87qkqLYcKf6P2CeYo9jWWq3Es8WIIelM0eNWaIM5gku6B_MLpLRAXr57JXjwarV-kTwCsQGjOFpk8E72i3ryhJ0eMdTjCKeLU1SF2glkz6inRYSB7fDHwTzxe3DPz, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHatGq9zUHbd-wlNefvLyhL7qmODSlFZEGuldqiZ4G-Bzts8V6aeGvhX2zs_AdurP07D7gEZB4oenok8-HXWdSD9pu7if7grVjQ5bBuFKrSjNJc2Syx1e0dicXrWfft3f9XYL4OYn63q6a4fZGiuTzYjZQtPHw).\n*   **Distribution by Region (2024):** **61% of bottles sold worldwide were distributed in Europe**, and **14% in Latin America and Canada** (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9YJlMJnKOnsPunUJIKTMp4pjm2MLCz1e6k4m1CtJoIF-L5T7O6IG76CmNymhSiSV_yvo5LiuwA6LJV8DOzsvMTc87qkqLYcKf6P2CeYo9jWWq3Es8WIIelM0eNWaIM5gku6B_MLpLRAXr57JXjwarV-kTwCsQGjOFpk8E72i3ryhJ0eMdTjCKeLU1SF2glkz6inRYSB7fDHwTzxe3DPz, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHatGq9zUHbd-wlNefvLyhL7qmODSlFZEGuldqiZ4G-Bzts8V6aeGvhX2zs_AdurP07D7gEZB4oenok8-HXWdSD9pu7if7grVjQ5bBuFKrSjNJc2Syx1e0dicXrWfft3f9XYL4OYn63q6a4fZGiuTzYjZQtPHw).\n*   **Export vs. Domestic Sales:** Exports account for approximately **80% of its sales**, with sales in Cuba accounting for approximately **20%** (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9YJlMJnKOnsPunUJIKTMp4pjm2MLCz1e6k4m1CtJoIF-L5T7O6IG76CmNymhSiSV_yvo5LiuwA6LJV8DOzsvMTc87qkqLYcKf6P2CeYo9jWWq3Es8WIIelM0eNWaIM5gku6B_MLpLRAXr57JXjwarV-kTwCsQGjOFpk8E72i3ryhJ0eMdTjCKeLU1SF2glkz6inRYSB7fDHwTzxe3DPz, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHatGq9zUHbd-wlNefvLyhL7qmODSlFZEGuldqiZ4G-Bzts8V6aeGvhX2zs_AdurP07D7gEZB4oenok8-HXWdSD9pu7if7grVjQ5bBuFKrSjNJc2Syx1e0dicXrWfft3f9XYL4OYn63q6a4fZGiuTzYjZQtPHw).\n*   **Future Targets:** Havana Club aims to reach **six million cases by 2028**, with **one million cases from the super-premium segment** by the same year (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9YJlMJnKOnsPunUJIKTMp4pjm2MLCz1e6k4m1CtJoIF-L5T7O6IG76CmNymhSiSV_yvo5LiuwA6LJV8DOzsvMTc87qkqLYcKf6P2CeYo9jWWq3Es8WIIelM0eNWaIM5gku6B_MLpLRAXr57JXjwarV-kTwCsQGjOFpk8E72i3ryhJ0eMdTjCKeLU1SF2glkz6inRYSB7fDHwTzxe3DPz, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHatGq9zUHbd-wlNefvLyhL7qmODSlFZEGuldqiZ4G-Bzts8V6aeGvhX2zs_AdurP07D7gEZB4oenok8-HXWdSD9pu7if7grVjQ5bBuFKrSjNJc2Syx1e0dicXrWfft3f9XYL4OYn63q6a4fZGiuTzYjZQtPHw).\n*   **Projected Deceleration (FY25):** Havana Club's growth is projected to decelerate to **+1% in value in fiscal year 2025** (ending June 2025) (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHatGq9zUHbd-wlNefvLyhL7qmODSlFZEGuldqiZ4G-Bzts8V6aeGvhX2zs_AdurP07D7gEZB4oenok8-HXWdSD9pu7if7grVjQ5bBuFKrSjNJc2Syx1e0dicXrWfft3f9XYL4OYn63q6a4fZGiuTzYjZQtPHw, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE9YJlMJnKOnsPunUJIKTMp4pjm2MLCz1e6k4m1CtJoIF-L5T7O6IG76CmNymhSiSV_yvo5LiuwA6LJV8DOzsvMTc87qkqLYcKf6P2CeYo9jWWq3Es8WIIelM0eNWaIM5gku6B_MLpLRAXr57JXjwarV-kTwCsQGjOFpk8E72i3ryhJ0eMdTjCKeLU1SF2glkz6inRYSB7fDHwTzxe3DPz). Havana Club experienced a decline in sales volume and value in fiscal year 2025 and the first half of fiscal year 2026. Sales declined by **8% in volume and 12% in value in FY25** (ending June 2025). Sales decreased by **16% in the first half of fiscal year 2026** (July-December 2025) [https://www.pernod-ricard.com/sites/default/files/2025-08/FY25%20Sales%20and%20Results%20Presentation.pdf, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2026/02/china-and-us-hinder-pernod-h1-sales/].\n\n---\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"STRATEGIC SYNTHESIS — SO WHAT FOR LIQUID & THE BRAND","content":"\nHavana Club, under Pernod Ricard, is a brand with deep historical roots, a strong premium positioning, and a clear strategic direction towards high-value growth and youth engagement. However, it operates within a complex geopolitical landscape and faces specific market challenges and opportunities.\n\n**What is Left on the Table (Opportunities):**\n\n1.  **Untapped US Market (Latent Fit):** The most significant \"left on the table\" opportunity is the US market. While legally inaccessible to Pernod Ricard's Havana Club, the existing Bacardi version and the ongoing trademark battle highlight a strong latent demand for \"Havana Club\" rum. Should the political landscape shift, or a resolution be reached, Pernod Ricard stands to gain immense market share. Even without direct sales, the US market represents a significant cultural influence pool. The financial opportunity cost due to the US embargo on Cuban-produced Havana Club is estimated to be **20 million bottles annually** in lost sales for Pernod Ricard [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF92P1F_e80hbsCLmWOcoCRQUdBWNLK-j71G8cgA_gDYJ-PBxEWuLBlBRx1dOkYZ5_lX7xFepPMzyWQW0EFCsdPf6mQ8XLEh6MjRqbxj0OSu7a09Sxr4QIXcY4296g6x1VQma-xEXv1jF-OKDhaRA9k-Fc073iXf0Eo5377SXawrNY1rZe4WjoqtusVzQ==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGfQiUYa8tUDilOejL5o0OL4igp5XMkwmOnANNe4v9mCUWXf3x8hh78OMmiT7_Tp39iI2T8LMAeNr3CMN5Cm5bXzKhVdgDMJo8a-KUAb8V2Yr2aXKEi--18Hlg34VUKbYEVf1ypwNjK0KNvKQOG3afQQVq9_guRF0ROYPKyG5UWM8QLje5DGv-qOIwVMa6auyAsLksVlhFpTP6qCLYbGmAFsMN-ftT]. The US rum market was valued at approximately **USD 2.91 billion in 2024** and is projected to reach **USD 3.86 billion by 2030**, growing at a CAGR of **4.9% from 2025 to 2030** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFH7t0ckrPdVvs9RBZRX0mdvx6r7oyC_j-oQXctuwGnpd4wsE0dR0LK3VNgsShsIvJR2C2gc4UD6v84eDwI6iRSO6KHdr9-CMUDUp1FofK8ZcZO6F18cWytv-4hQr_MfKnK_gcqU1NgDkMXYaBSMHgEgJdYvKI1GaXHY3X06nfEFq1WFg==\", https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGLnaXdziYzvVS6uUq3U5apjJeeTzuEAtoQthKFdOQl2DmTvWk68ECeg9Pcli4leMyla2BW6Osbej7A7157XweMsGV8fIWLkQgNLrgwTHYd3pmK4BGFjACjKC-CzMF65UCVdH8vlQpO1_2mM92BQuhB69HXS6pqK8sxTXazJG-57GnsWly3]. A conservative **10-15% market share** for Havana Club in the US market would represent an\n"}]
